> Stevie D (aka Bloo) <blueboy@bu.edu> said,

> >Glenn Grant wrote:
> >
> >> Another problem is ebullism - see my accompanying post on vac exposure. Gas
> >> bubbles in the blood might kill a PC even if recompression is quickly
